OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FHelen Ford sat with Jo-Anne Cohrs to
OL,7,Fwatch the 1975 World in Action
OL,8,Finterview featuring her late husband
OL,10,FThe widow of a North East victim of
OL,11,Fthe contaminated blood scandal
OL,12,Frecalled the "quiet terror" he felt
OL,13,Fafter learning he had contracted HIV,
OL,14,Fas she watched his interview for a
OL,15,F1975 documentary.
OL,17,FJo-Anne Cohrs's husband Keith Proud
OL,18,Fdied in 1987 at the age of 38 - just
OL,19,Ffour years after the pair married.
