OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FMr Proud was treated for severe
OL,7,Fhaemophilia with infected blood
OL,8,Fproducts to control his bleeding. This
OL,9,Fled to him contracting hepatitis and
OL,10,Flater HIV.
OL,12,FIn 1975, the ITV documentary series
OL,13,FWorld in Action investigated the
OL,14,Fpotential dangers of contaminated
OL,15,Fblood products imported from the
OL,16,FUnited States. Among those interviewed
OL,17,Fwas Mr Proud.
