OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FFive decades on and ahead of the
OL,7,Freport into the Infected Blood Inquiry
OL,8,Fbeing published, Ms Cohrs sat down to
OL,9,Fwatch her late husband in the
OL,10,Fdocumentary.
OL,12,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees that this
OL,13,Fbrought back the "quiet terror, panic
OL,14,Fand fear" her partner felt on learning
OL,15,Fof his HIV diagnosis.
OL,17,F"We were married and ready to face
OL,18,Flife, and then this news came along,"
OL,19,FMs Cohrs added.
