OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FThe film makers travelled to the US,
OL,7,Fto demonstrate how donors - many from
OL,8,Fhigh risk groups - were paid to give
OL,9,Fblood plasma.
OL,11,FMr Proud had recently been diagnosed
OL,12,Fwith a form of the liver condition,
OL,13,Fhepatitis, linked to his treatment
OL,14,Fwhen he was featured.
OL,16,FHe explained in the documentary: "It
OL,17,Fstarted off with backache, thing like
OL,18,Fthat, feeling pretty rotten, a couple
OL,19,Fof days later I started to turn
OL,20,Fyellow, the whites of my eyes started
OL,21,Fto turn yellow ..."
