OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FIn the film Mr Proud is asked whether
OL,7,Fhe would prefer to use a product made
OL,8,Ffrom voluntary blood donors in Britain.
OL,10,F"Obviously that would be better but
OL,11,Funtil that is available, we have to
OL,12,Faccept the risks," he answers.
OL,14,FMs Cohrs, who now lives in Washingon
OL,15,Fon Wearside, said her late husband was
OL,16,F"resigned" to the dilemma of balancing
OL,17,Fhis need for treatment - and the risks
OL,18,Fassociated with it.
