OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,F"He was stuck really because without
OL,7,Fany treatment he would have to visit
OL,8,Fthe hospital ward at least once a
OL,9,Fweek, three times a month with a
OL,10,Fsevere bleed - uncontrollable bleed,"
OL,11,Fshe explained.
OL,13,F"He didn't have an option. He wouldn't
OL,14,Fhave had a life."
OL,16,FIn the aftermath of her husband's
OL,17,Fdeath Ms Cohrs wrote a book detailing
OL,18,Fhow her Christian faith and community
OL,19,Fguided her through.
