OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FEntitled 'Stigma -An AIDS Widow's
OL,7,FStory', it highlights the attitudes
OL,8,Fthe couple experienced around Keith's
OL,9,Fdiagnosis.JLittle did Ms Cohrs realise
OL,10,Fat the time that their story would
OL,11,Fform part of the biggest treatment
OL,12,Fdisaster in UK history.
OL,14,FMs Cohrs said her greatest hope now is
OL,15,Fthat lessons are learned from the
OL,16,Fscandal to protect the patients - like
OL,17,Fher late husband - of the future.
OL,19,FThe final report: what has changed for
OL,20,FJo-Anne Cohrs?
