OL,3,CWorld in Action interview brings back
OL,4,C'quiet terror' of late husband's HIV
OL,6,FShe hopes the findings will also
OL,7,Fprovide some comfort for people who
OL,8,Fare still facing the prospect of their
OL,9,Fown death, or that of a loved one, as
OL,10,Fa result of the disaster.
OL,12,FMs Cohrs also senses a sea change,
OL,13,Fbelieving that the conclusions could
OL,14,Fchange the way law makers and those in
OL,15,Fthe health industry operate, to ensure
OL,16,Fa scandal of this kind cannot happen
OL,17,Fagain.
